      • updateBtDevice

        public void updateBtDevice(BluetoothDevice device)
        zh:

        更新蓝牙设备信对象。

        蓝牙设备对象信息发生变化调用次方法更新Device设备对应信息,此方法有sdk内部调用维护。 This method has an internal call to the sdk.

        en:

        Update Bluetooth device info.

        The change of the object information of the Bluetooth device is changed to update the corresponding information of the Device device.

        参数:
        device - 蓝牙设备 Bluetooth device

      • updateRssi

        public void updateRssi(int rssi)
        zh:

        更新信号强度。

        设备信号值rssi 发生变化时调用此方法，会重新计算距离，此方法有sdk内部调用维护。

        en:

        Update signal strength.

        Call this method when the signal value of the device is changed, and the distance is calculated by the RSSI. This method has an internal call to the sdk.

        参数:
        rssi - 信号强度
